      <abstract obkms_id="f1efd48c-0550-47c1-8299-e79a980d8fea" obkms_process="TRUE">
        <label>Abstract</label>
        <p>A new subpecies, <tp:taxon-name obkms_id="8568b461-de92-4785-a2d4-0505768720c6" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Tulipa</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">cinnabarina</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="infraspecific-rank">subsp.</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="subspecies">toprakii</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name> <bold>subsp. nov.</bold> (<tp:taxon-name obkms_id="cce22d98-d563-4211-b6ee-f48fe69eac0f" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="family">Liliaceae</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name>) from Turkey is described. Diagnostic characters, descriptions, detailed illustrations, geographical distribution, conservation status and ecological observations on the new taxon are provided. It is also compared with the closely related <tp:taxon-name obkms_id="7e54d5e5-670d-40e6-9619-229b7cb25ec1" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Tulipa</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">cinnabarina</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="infraspecific-rank">subsp.</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="subspecies">cinnabarina</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name>.</p>
      </abstract>
